  <name>Sharly Chess</name>
  <summary>Tournament Management System for Chess</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Sharly Chess is a comprehensive application designed for chess arbiters
      and tournament organizers to manage all aspects of chess tournaments.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Tournament creation and management</li>
      <li>Player registration and categorization</li>
      <li>Pairing generation (Swiss, Round-robin systems)</li>
      <li>Real-time result display</li>
      <li>Scoring and tie-break calculations</li>
      <li>Export to Chess-Results, FFE, and other formats</li>
      <li>Multi-language support (French, English)</li>
      <li>Integration with chess federations (FFE, FIDE)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

